'''Adzo''' alo '''Adzowo''' (si woyɔna le Eŋlisigbeme be '''[[:en:Riddle|Riddle]]''') nye nya kpui aɖewo  si wogblɔna tsɔna doa ame ƒe susu kpɔ, eye eƒe gɔmesese be ɖe eme. Kɔsasa alo babla nɔa adzowo ŋu. Amewo dzea agbagba desiade tua kɔsasa sia, si fia kɔtɔe be woɖe egɔme.

==Adzo ƒe vevie nyenyewo==
