#Miesrɔa nulele ɖe tame.
#Miesrɔa nuƒoƒo le amedome.
#Miesrɔa sedziwɔwɔ.
#Mesrɔa tamebubu
#Ɖekawɔwɔ va ɖeviwo dome.
#Miesrɔa hadome gbenɔnɔ.

